        public UpgradeResourceFilter.Builder setValues​(java.util.List<java.lang.String> values)
        Values to be searched. For searching exact string use simple string e.g. Cluster-1 , for wildcard , use *Cluster*1*. This values are Or'ed while filtering i.e. if resource matches any of the value in array (case-insensitive) then it will be returned.
